track_notes: The most popular route to Rabun Bald.  Very limited parking available at Beegum Gap.  Please do not block any driveways.
track_title: W4C/NG-002 - Rabun Bald from Beegum Gap

track_notes: Alternate route from Beegum Gap and meets up with the trail about half way up.  Use it as an alternative route or if you have a high-clearance 4WD vehicle (that you dont mind getting scratched), you can cut your hike in half.
track_title: W4C/NG-002 - Rabun Bald - Jeep Road from Beegum Gap
